imdb.plot outline: Dutch Profiles is a series of short documentaries about architects and graphic, product and fashion designers in the Netherlands, commissioned by DutchDFA. Dutch Profiles includes interviews with, among others: Rem Koolhaas, Hella Jongerius, Droog Design, Jurgen Bey, Claudy Jongstra, Wim Crouwel, Marlies Dekkers, Alexander van Slobbe and G-Star.
